\v 1 Ngathi mina enhliziyweni yami: Woza-ke, ngizakuzama ngentokozo, njalo kholisa okuhle. Khangela-ke, lalokhu kwakuyize\x + 3.13. 5.18. 6.6. 9.9. 2.24. Hlab. 34.12.\x*.
\v 2 Ngokuhleka ngathi\x + 7.6. Zaga 14.13.\x*: Kuyibuhlanya! Langentokozo: Kwenzani\x + Hlab. 102.8.\x*?
\v 3 Ngadinga enhliziyweni yami ukuthokozisa\f + \fk ukuthokozisa: \fl Heb. \fq ukudonsa.\f* inyama yami ngewayini\x + 1.17.\x* (kodwa ngakhokhela inhliziyo yami ngenhlakanipho\x + 2.9.\x*), lokubambelela ebuthutheni, ngize ngibone ukuthi kuyini lokho okulungele abantwana babantu, abangakwenza ngaphansi kwamazulu, ngenani lensuku zempilo zabo\x + 2.12,13. 7.25. 10.1,13. 1.17.\x*.
