\v 4 Ngazenzela imisebenzi emikhulu; ngazakhela izindlu\x + 1 Kho. 7.1-12.\x*; ngazihlanyelela izivini;
\v 5 ngazenzela izivande lezivande zezihlahla; ngahlanyela kuzo izihlahla zezithelo zohlobo lonke\x + Neh. 2.8.\x*;
\v 6 ngazenzela amachibi amanzi okuthelela ngawo ihlathi lokukhulisa izihlahla;
\v 7 ngathenga izigqili lezigqilikazi, ngaba labazalelwe\f + \fk labazalelwe: \fl Heb. \fq abantwana.\f* endlini\x + Zaga 8.22.\x*; njalo ngaba lemfuyo enengi yenkomo lezimvu\x + 1 Kho. 4.23.\x* okwedlula bonke ababekhona ngaphambi kwami eJerusalema\x + 1.12.\x*;
\v 8 ngazibuthela futhi isiliva legolide\x + 1 Kho. 9.28. 10.10,14,21.\x* lemfuyo ekhethekileyo\x + Eks. 19.5.\x* yamakhosi\x + 1 Kho. 4.21. 10.15.\x* leyamazwe\x + 5.8. 1 Kho. 20.14. Lilo 1.1. Hez. 19.8.\x*; ngazizuzela abahlabeleli labahlabelelikazi\x + 2 Sam. 19.35. 2 Lan. 35.25.\x*, lentokozo zabantwana babantu, amantombazana emihlobo yonke\f + \fk izinto zokuhlabelela zemihlobo yonke: \fl Heb. \fq into yokuhlabelela lezinto zokuhlabelela.\f*\x + Zaga 19.10.\x*.
\v 9 Ngakho ngaba mkhulu nganda okwedlula wonke owayekhona ngaphambi kwami\x + 1.16. 1 Lan. 29.25.\x* eJerusalema\x + 1.12.\x*, lenhlakanipho yami yema lami\x + 2.3.\x*.
\v 10 Lakho konke amehlo ami akufisayo kangiwancitshanga khona, kangigodlanga inhliziyo yami lakuyiphi intokozo; ngoba inhliziyo yami yathokoza ekutshikatshikeni kwami konke\x + Nani 11.17.\x*; lalokhu kwaba yisabelo sami somtshikatshika wami wonke\x + 3.22. 5.18. 9.9.\x*.
\v 11 Mina ngasengikhangela yonke imisebenzi izandla zami eziyenzileyo, lomtshikatshika engangitshikatshike ukuwenza; khangela-ke, konke kwakuyize lokukhathazeka komoya\x + 1.14.\x*, njalo kwakungekho nzuzo ngaphansi kwelanga\x + 1.3.\x*.
\p
\v 12 Mina ngasengibuyela ukubona inhlakanipho lobuhlanya\x + 7.25. 1.17.\x* lobuthutha\x + 2.3.\x*. Ngoba a\add ngenza\add*ni umuntu olandela inkosi\x + 2.18.\x*? Lokho\x + 1.9.\x* okuvele sekwenziwe\x + 1.10.\x*.
\v 13 Mina ngasengibona ukuthi inhlakanipho ingcono\f + \fk ingcono: \fl Heb. \fq ilobuhle obukhulu.\f* kulobuthutha\x + 2.3.\x* njengokukhanya kungcono kulomnyama\x + 1.3.\x*.
\v 14 Ohlakaniphileyo, amehlo akhe asekhanda lakhe, kodwa isithutha sihamba emnyameni\x + 8.1. Zaga 17.24.\x*; ngasengisazi lami ukuthi isehlakalo sinye sehlela bonke\x + Hlab. 49.10.\x*\x + 3.19. 9.2,3,11. 2.15.\x*.
\v 15 Mina ngasengisithi enhliziyweni yami: Njengoba kusehlela isithutha kuzangehlela lami\x + 3.19. 9.2,3,11. 2.15.\x*; pho, kungani-ke mina ngangihlakaniphe okwedlulisileyo? Ngasengikhuluma enhliziyweni yami ukuthi lokhu lakho kuyize\x + 6.8,11. 7.11,16. 12.9,12. Esta 6.6.\x*.
\v 16 Ngoba kakukho ukukhunjulwa kohlakaniphileyo okwedlula koyisithutha phakade\x + 1.11.\x*; ngoba lokhu okukhona khathesi ensukwini ezizayo konke kuzakhohlakala\x + 1.10.\x*. Ohlakaniphileyo ufa njani? Njengesithutha\x + Hlab. 49.10.\x*.
\v 17 Ngasengizonda impilo, ngoba umsebenzi owenziwa ngaphansi kwelanga wawubuhlungu kimi; ngoba konke kuyize lokukhathazeka komoya\x + 1.14.\x*.
\v 18 Yebo, mina ngawuzonda wonke umtshikatshika wami engawutshikatshika ngaphansi kwelanga, ngoba ngizawutshiyela umuntu\x + Hlab. 39.6.\x* ozakuba khona ngemva kwami\x + 2.12.\x*.
\v 19 Ngubani-ke owaziyo ukuthi uzakuba ngohlakaniphileyo kumbe oyisithutha\x + Hlab. 39.6.\x*? Kanti uzabusa phezu kwawo wonke umtshikatshika wami engawutshikatshikayo lengiwenze ngenhlakanipho ngaphansi kwelanga. Lokhu lakho kuyize.
\p
\v 20 Mina ngasengiphenduka ngadangalisa inhliziyo yami ngomtshikatshika wonke engangiwutshikatshika ngaphansi kwelanga\x + 7.25.\x*.
\v 21 Ngoba kulomuntu omtshikatshika wakhe ukunhlakanipho lakulwazi lakubuqotho, kanti uzawunika umuntu ongatshikatshikanga kuwo ube yisabelo sakhe. Lokhu lakho kuyize, lobubi obukhulu\x + 4.4. 5.11. 11.6.\x*.
\v 22 Ngoba ulani umuntu ngomtshikatshika wakhe wonke\x + 1.3. 3.9.\x* langokukhathazeka kwenhliziyo yakhe akutshikatshike ngaphansi kwelanga\x + 1.14.\x*?
\v 23 Ngoba insuku zakhe\x + Jobe 14.1.\x* zonke zizinsizi\x + 1.18.\x*, lomsebenzi wakhe\x + 1.13.\x* uyikudabuka; lebusuku inhliziyo yakhe kayiphumuli. Lokhu lakho kuyize\x + 1.18.\x*.
