\v 24 Kakukho okungcono emuntwini \add kul\add*okuthi adle anathe\x + 3.12,13,22. 5.18. 8.15. 9.7,11. Luka 12.19. 1 Kor. 15.32. 1 Tim. 6.17.\x* abonise umphefumulo wakhe okuhle emtshikatshikeni wakhe\x + 2.1.\x*. Lokhu lakho mina ngabona ukuthi kuvela esandleni sikaNkulunkulu\x + 3.13.\x*.
\v 25 Ngoba ngubani ongadla kumbe ngubani ongakholisa kulami?
